e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> acquire most of OpenAI=E2=80=99s st=
aff</a>=C2=A0without paying the company (or its other investors) anything f=
or them.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But then there was another boardroom coup, Alt=
man <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33498739.28642=
9/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTEtMjIvc2FtL=
WFsdG1hbi10by1yZXR1cm4tYXMtb3BlbmFpLWNlby13aXRoLWEtbmV3LWJvYXJkP2NtcGlkPUJC=
RDExMjcyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGV=
yJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTEyNyZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a31=
9a23cB51bdf4bb" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_b=
lank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bot=
tom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; b=
ackground-color: #ccc;">  got his job back</a>, and most of the directors w=
ho fired him were themselves fired. Altman returned, and there have been su=
ggestions that he=C2=A0(and Microsoft, OpenAI=E2=80=99s biggest investor) e=
xtracted some promises=C2=A0that this sort of thing won=E2=80=99t be allowe=
d to happen again, that there will be fundamental governance changes to mak=
e OpenAI more robust and, probably, more commercial.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So how much should OpenAI be worth=C2=A0<em>to=
day?=C2=A0</em>Some possible answers:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Less than $86 billion, for governance=
 reasons: After a rapid rise in prominence and valuation, OpenAI revealed s=
ome serious cracks,=C2=A0<em>causing its valuation to become zero dollars f=
or a while</em>, meaning that investors should be far more cautious about i=
t now than they were before. It is more volatile than people thought. The l=
esson of the last week, I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/33498739.286429/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGl=
