XRtX3Rlcm09MjMxMTI3JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23=
cB8aa1de35" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank=
" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-=
width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backg=
round-color: #ccc;"> suggested on Tuesday</a>, might be =E2=80=9Cdon=E2=80=
=99t invest in nonprofits at an $86 billion valuation=E2=80=9D; maybe inves=
tors will learn that lesson.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;"=
>More than $86 billion, for governance reasons: Those cracks were there fro=
m the beginning, and investors presumably accounted for them in that $86 bi=
llion valuation. But now that Altman has won his power struggle and <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33498739.286429/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnNpZGVyLmNvbS9zYW0tYWx0bWFuLW9wZW5haS1zdGFmZi1sb3lhbHR5=
LXBvd2VyLWNoYXRncHQtbWljcm9zb2Z0LTIwMjMtMTE_dXRtX21lZGl1bT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV=
0bV9zb3VyY2U9U2FpbHRocnUmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPUluc2lkZXJfVG9kYXk/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cBf8ff672a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> cemented his control</a>, the future OpenAI =
<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33498739.286429/aH=
R0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS90ZWNoL2FpL2FpLWFjY2VsZXJhdGlvbmlzdHMtY29tZS1vdXQtY=
WhlYWQtd2l0aC1zYW0tYWx0bWFucy1yZXR1cm4tdG8tb3BlbmFpLWEyNDk2MDVj/607f07ceef4=
b8524a319a23cBe18689c5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;"> will be=C2=A0<em>less=C2=A0</em>weird and =
nonprofit-y</a> and afraid of its own shadow. It=E2=80=99s the same excitin=
g business but with better, more investor-friendly governance, so it should=
 be worth more to investors.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Less =
than $86 billion, for governance reasons (2): <em>Did=C2=A0</em>Altman win =
his power struggle? Ten days ago, he was the CEO and a board member; now he=
 is off the board. Ben Thompson <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/33498739.286429/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdHJhdGVjaGVyeS5jb20vMjAyMy9zYW0tY=
Wx0bWFuLWJhY2stYXQtb3BlbmFpLXEtZ29pbmctZm9yd2FyZC8/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23c=
B91e175b2" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank"=
 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">quotes</a> a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/33498739.286429/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmVkZGl0LmNvbS9yL01hY2hpbmVMZ=
