om-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; ba=
ckground-color: #ccc;"> Reddit post</a> arguing that the drama was precipit=
ated by <em>Altman=E2=80=99s=C2=A0</em>efforts to seize total control of th=
e board, and that the other board members outmaneuvered him, with the resul=
t that his power has been diminished. The other board members =E2=80=9Cget =
the outcome they want: Sam and Greg [Brockman] gone from the board; Adam [D=
=E2=80=99Angelo] remains, who has experience of Sam and Greg=E2=80=99s shen=
anigans; and two mutually agreeable independent board members are added=E2=
=80=9D who will presumably rein in Altman.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-botto=
m: 5px;">More than $86 billion, for governance reasons (2): Maybe a board t=
hat reins in Altman will start by reining in his <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33498739.286429/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
LmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTEtMTkvYWx0bWFuLXNvdWdodC1iaWxsaW9ucy1mb3I=
