"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;">  extracurricular AI-related business ventures</a> (a chip compan=
y, =E2=80=9Can AI-focused hardware device=E2=80=9D) and make him focus more=
 on OpenAI, which will be good for the company. =E2=80=9CWhen Altman return=
s, he=E2=80=99ll likely have to address claims that he=E2=80=99s been distr=
acted by a number of projects, including those outside OpenAI,=E2=80=9D <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33498739.286429/aHR0c=
HM6Ly93d3cudGhlaW5mb3JtYXRpb24uY29tL2FydGljbGVzL3doYXQtY29tZXMtbmV4dC1mb3It=
c2FtLWFsdG1hbnMtb3BlbmFp/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5e5713ef" itemprop=3D"Sto=
