lid; background-color: #ccc;">  appealing feature=C2=A0of private market in=
vestments</a>: They are less volatile than public investments, because when=
 dramatic shifts in markets or fundamentals happen,=C2=A0<em>you can ignore=
 them=C2=A0</em>and just say that the value of your private investments is =
miraculously unchanged. Without a market price, you never need to mark to m=
arket.=C2=A0It would be very, very funny if the events of the last 10 days =
