e compliance employee wrote, =E2=80=9Cwe need a banner =E2=80=98is washing =
drug money too hard these days - come to binance we got cake for you.=E2=80=
=99=E2=80=9D Due in part to Binance=E2=80=99s failure to implement an effec=
tive AML program, illicit actors used Binance=E2=80=99s exchange in various=
 ways, including conducting transactions for mixing services that obfuscate=
d the source and ownership of cryptocurrency; transferring illicit proceeds=
 from ransomware variants; and moving proceeds of darknet market transactio=
ns, exchange hacks, and various internet-related scams.</p>
</blockquote>
